filter.expression: (http.request.version in {"HTTP/1.0" "HTTP/1.1" "HTTP/1.2" "HTTP/2" "HTTP/3"} and http.request.uri.path in {"/contact/" "/contact" "/en/contact" "/sign-up" "/get-in-touch"} and not http.user_agent contains "Googlebot" and not http.user_agent contains "Bingbot" and not http.user_agent contains "DuckDuckBot" and not http.user_agent contains "facebot" and not http.user_agent contains "Slurp" and not http.user_agent contains "Alexa")
